p]], for $160 million.<ref>{{cite news|last1=Arora|first1=Varun|title=We will set up family office soon, says Bhavin Turakhia|url=http://www.vccircle.com/news/media-entertainment/2016/08/26/we-will-set-family-office-soon-says-bhavin-turakhia|publisher=[[VCCircle]]|date=26 August 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Modgil|first1=Shweta|title=It's Our Moral Obligation To Make An Impact Directly Proportional To Our Potential: Bhavin Turakhia, Co-Founder, Directi Group|url=https://inc42.com/startups/interviews/bhavin-turakhia-directi/|accessdate=24 March 2017|publisher=Inc42.com|date=10 January 2017}}</ref>\n\nHe currently operates [[Flock (messaging service)|Flock]],<ref>{{cite news|last1=Shaikh|first1=Shadma|title=Bhavin Turakhia invests $25 mn in enterprise messenger Flock for expansion|url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/small-biz/money/bhavin-turakhia-invests-25-mn-in-enterprise-messenger-flock-for-expansion/articleshow/57654006.cms|accessdate=24 March 2017|publisher=[[The Economic Times|Economic Times]]|date=16 March 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Singh|first1=Arti|title=Bhavin Turakhia to invest $25 mn more in enterprise messenger Flock|url=http://www.vccircle.com/news/technology/2017/03/16/bhavin-turakhia-adds-25-mn-more-enterprise-messenger-flock-expansion?logintype=premium|publisher=[[VCCircle]]|date=16 March 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=VENTURE DEALS|url=http://fortune.com/2017/03/16/term-sheet-thursday-march-16/|publisher=[[Fortune (magazine)|Fortune]]|date=16 March 2016}}</ref> [[Ringo (software)|Ringo]], Radix and [[Zeta India |Zeta]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Personally Tech With Ringo Founder-CEO Bhavin Turakhia|url=http://gadgets.ndtv.com/apps/features/personally-tech-with-ringo-founder-ceo-bhavin-turakhia-719339|publisher=[[NDTV]]|date=24 July 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Mendonca|first1=Jochelle|title=Directi's Bhavin Turakhia to invest $110 million in newer ventures|url=http://tech.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/startups/directis-b